---
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
import LandingPage from '../../layouts/LandingPage.astro';
import tugScheduleScreenshot from '../../assets/features/tug-schedule-screenshot.png';
import tugMathprogScreenshot from '../../assets/features/tug-mathprog-screenshot.png';
---
<LandingPage 
  title="Intelligent Tugboat Scheduling" 
  description="Optimize your fleet operations. Reduce idle time, cut fuel costs, and ensure perfect timing with our predictive tugboat scheduling algorithms."
>
  <div class="hero-screenshot">
    <Image src={tugScheduleScreenshot} alt="PortTracker Tug Plan showing LP-optimized tugboat scheduling with Gantt chart timeline for Hamburg port fleet" width={1200} quality={85} />
  </div>

  <div class="feature-block">
    <div class="feature-text">
      <h2>Predictive Job Allocation</h2>
      <p>Using advanced linear programming and live AIS data, PortTracker predicts exactly when a vessel will arrive at the pilot station and assigns the optimal tugboat to the job, minimizing fuel burn and idle waiting times.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="feature-image">🚜</div>
  </div>

  <div class="feature-block reverse">
    <div class="feature-text">
      <h2>Mathematical Optimization Under the Hood</h2>
      <p>Our scheduling engine uses GNU MathProg to solve a real linear program — factoring in bollard pull demand, tug substitution, time windows, travel between berths, and duty limits. You can even inspect and edit the optimization model live.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="screenshot-inline">
      <Image src={tugMathprogScreenshot} alt="GNU MathProg optimization model used for tugboat scheduling in PortTracker" width={900} quality={85} />
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="feature-block">
    <div class="feature-text">
      <h2>Live Fleet Tracking</h2>
      <p>Keep an eye on your entire tug fleet in real-time. Know exactly which tugs are currently engaged, which are on standby, and view their precise operational status and speeds directly on the live map.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="feature-image">⚓</div>
  </div>
</LandingPage>

<style>
  .hero-screenshot {
    margin: -2rem auto 3rem;
    max-width: 1100px;
    border-radius: 12px;
    overflow: hidden;
    box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);
    border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
  }
  .hero-screenshot img {
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    display: block;
  }
  .screenshot-inline {
    flex: 1;
    border-radius: 12px;
    overflow: hidden;
    box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
    border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
  }
  .screenshot-inline img {
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    display: block;
  }
</style>
